T1  - The health of Latino children: urgent priorities, unanswered questions, and a research agenda.
T3  - Erratum in: JAMA. 2003 Aug 13;290(6):756 Note: Gomez, Francisco R [corrected to Ramos-Gomez, Francisco J]Comment in: JAMA. 2002 Oct 23-30;288(16):1982-3; author reply 1983. PMID: 12387640 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12387640] Comment in: JAMA. 2002 Oct 23-30;288(16):1983; author reply 1983. PMID: 12387641 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12387641] Comment in: JAMA. 2002 Oct 23-30;288(16):1981-2; author reply 1983. PMID: 12387642 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12387642] Comment in: JAMA. 2002 Oct 23-30;288(16):1981; author reply 1983. PMID: 12387643 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12387643]
